items.title: Remnantknights Wiki
items.headline: Welcome to the Remnant Knights Wiki!
items.desc: Welcome to the Remnant Knights Wiki, your online resource for everything Remnant Knights! Remnant Knights is a free to play, casual MMO for teens and the young at heart. Come join with your friends, as students of either Owl or Dragon Schools, and fulfill your destiny as one of the mighty Knights of Kasmari!

items.name: The Big Knights Wiki
items.title: The Big Knights Wiki
items.headline: Learn more about The Big Knights!
items.desc: British animated series The Big Knights premiered on the BBC in 1999. Since then, it has developed a cult following around the world, despite only having been shown in four countries! The Big Knights is arguably more popular now than when it was first released, and a feature film spin-off is now in production.

items.desc: This is a Wiki about people who love playing games. We're promotive for people and we love playing games. There's not a lot of games but we love having new members and reviewing games. Explore dozens of randomly-generated islands and restore peace to a world torn apart by The Fracture.

items.name: Arknights Wiki
items.title: Arknights Wiki
items.desc: Arknights (明日方舟) is a Chinese mobile Tower Defense game. Players are in charge of the operatives of Rhodes Island to investigate natural disasters occurring due to the appearance of the mysterious Originium ore, while holding the front against violent groups infected by the said substance.
